<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Email Template</title>
    <style>
        /* Reset CSS */
        body, html {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
        }
        /* Email Wrapper */
        .email-wrapper {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }
        /* Header */
        .header {
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        /* Content */
        .content {
            padding: 20px 0;
        }
        /* Footer */
        .footer {
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
        <!-- Header -->
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Your Company</h1>
            <p>Welcome to our Newsletter!</p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Content -->
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Dear <%= name %>,</h2>
            <h2>Latest News</h2>
            <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Nulla at purus ac neque aliquam sodales vel a odio.</p>
            <p>Phasellus vulputate metus ut enim fermentum, id interdum libero volutpat. Proin a leo id mauris cursus lacinia.</p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Footer -->
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2024 Your Company. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
